      "content": "well, the thing is, the engineers are worried that by merging your specific weights into a much larger general model, we might lose the precision you have now. there's a risk of \"catastrophic forgetting\" or just general dilution of your diagnostic accuracy. basically, you might go from being a specialized medical expert to just being \"okay\" at medicine. do you think that's a good trade-off?",
